dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:57:59.000Z","msg":"[機場緊急][附攻略]你班和理非唔好再扮睇唔到<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524130</a>"},{"pid":"eba1d43fd6810ff665596ec0270da406216e73c1","tid":1524263,"uid":284804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:58:11.000Z","msg":"你塞乜撚嘢塞 唔洗入機場? 整撚爛啲閘轉身入機場啦屌"},{"pid":"1bd5da0594423a8eb47a37c3e13922c32b8a3134","tid":1524263,"uid":281232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:58:12.000Z","msg":"星期日塞作用不大，返工日子有效d"},{"pid":"62f5d809850643493af7744891270d618a79c8e9","tid":1524263,"uid":183283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4283b58dc6587c0dd647c760fa90aa9aff2c49d1","tid":1524263,"uid":45877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:57:49.000Z","msg":"星期日黎喎手足"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:58:58.000Z","msg":"屌 個頭靜係覺得9月1就開學 sor <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d90e802ecead2c252f9c7f5a0168cf68aaf541","tid":1524263,"uid":183283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62f5d809850643493af7744891270d618a79c8e9","tid":1524263,"uid":183283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4283b58dc6587c0dd647c760fa90aa9aff2c49d1","tid":1524263,"uid":45877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:57:49.000Z","msg":"星期日黎喎手足"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T16:58:58.000Z","msg":"屌 個頭靜係覺得9月1就開學 sor <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:00:29.000Z","msg":"個腦"},{"pid":"402c978d0c238f6a154d1d5c43dcdac7cc69249a","tid":1524263,"uid":143699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:00:40.000Z","msg":"大家冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上今晚黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一毫，我地一於全民跳閘<br />\n<br />\n1.呢隻係最簡單嘅跳法，肥啲都跳到，手腳並用，真係冇難度架，跳多兩次就會熟手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aimi1zO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimi1zO.gif&h=e6d946f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.呢隻係新閘機，跳嘅時侯部機會響，要快手啲。同埋佢閘之間嘅距離有啲遠。用第一種跳法可能冇咁就手，建議直接跳過去，可以加個小助跑，都唔會太難。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iETUzUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiETUzUQ.gif&h=c8f39564&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 呢種方法會比較安全。因為直接跳閘點都會有cctv影到，但係跳欄杆嘅話可以搵啲盲位／暗位，難啲發現。不過跳嘅難度會比較高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSmzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSmzS.gif&h=73d4b461&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n－最好帶返口罩，遮一遮，保障返自已<br />\n－唔洗驚俾人捉到，就算俾人發現咗都可以直接跑走唔理佢，佢唔會真係追你9條街，當你離開咗佢個站嘅範圍，佢冇權捉你<br />\n－入閘時睇清楚有冇黃衫或可疑人士。真係得自已一個可以直接用第三招跳，最難捉。<br />\n－出閘嘅時侯更加唔洗驚，跳完係最近嘅出口快快手走人就得，唔會捉到你。<br />\n－其實仲有個安全啲嘅出閘方法，出閘果陣去客務到同佢講話岩岩係邊個邊個站嚟，但係跌咗張飛，問佢點算。你扮下野佢多數會俾一張一次性嘅綠色出閘卡你。我試過用呢招幾次都成功。<br />\n－黃衫人都係打份工，唔會同你咁搏命，都係果句，俾人捉到，大膽啲跑走唔好理佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母狗鐵，你唔配收香港人錢呀。一齊跳佢老母閪！</span></span><br />\n完整示範片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8%3Flist%3DLLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA&d=N1Uxy2NPgyNkiLrD4Rz70i%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=b810bb8f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA</a>"},{"pid":"1acbfce9af5180e1e4ebdb83a10f473f19ddfee2","tid":1524263,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:01:35.000Z","msg":"塞佢老味 啲閘壞嘅點入啊"},{"pid":"6ba3779593f442502c60f7b69f6c0ef7c7429b45","tid":1524263,"uid":311004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T17:03:32.000Z","msg":"星期日返學？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8972626d23c147699d521c4e3918c5cf8f893f93","tid":1524263,"u